{"id": 1698, "genre": 1000, "title": "你都有过哪些跟初衷完全走偏的体验？", "description": "人生总有那么些事与愿违（题图来自：Pixabay）", "record_count": 16348, "comment_count": 35, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20170519180812H0q6raDQdLbc5tkS.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2017-05-24T17:00:00Z", "questions": [{"id": 2346, "title": "你都有过哪些跟初衷完全走偏的体验？", "content": "你都有过哪些跟初衷完全走偏的体验？", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 205831, "content": "为了省时间订外卖，结果在翘首等待中焦急了一个多小时", "image": "img/option/option/20170521142941YJDfFAjOoGdIPyEN.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 205837, "content": "原本就想搜一条资料，结果扩展阅读了一下午段子", "image": "img/option/option/20170521143004tJ2hwD1539xeXGCR.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 205841, "content": "只想买一个杯子，结果下单满满一购物车的厨房用品（和零食）", "image": "img/option/option/20170521143029O1p7GbkaIBnuYDhf.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 205845, "content": "为了省时间叫车，结果等车的时间已经足够小跑到终点", "image": "img/option/option/20170525080416halnBo9FTS1CiPbw.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 205849, "content": "头脑风暴一不留神发散成大型闲聊", "image": "img/option/option/20170521144050UptIvrSe1Y854Jxo.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 205851, "content": "为了方便头发剪短，结果每天醒来头发都竖成毛利兰", "image": "img/option/option/20170521144343fjkT6Ly8OFU5azRX.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 205854, "content": "在咸鱼上想卖旧物，回应了200个“20卖不卖”的留言也没卖出去", "image": "img/option/option/20170521144329ZnvXa5Y04buxQBEP.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 205859, "content": "想开背景音调节工作气氛，结果时不时分心去点收藏", "image": "img/option/option/2017052114411951EPd6i27amhCqYr.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}